   I use a Nostromo, but I've never been banned for it. I've been using gamepads with EQ for almost 4 years now and I have never even been warned. <b>Of course</b> the rules are going to be interpeted by those who enforce them, that's the nature of the beast! I defenitely understand how you can be frustrated, I'm not telling you that your friend is a moron and deserves it, because a lot of the time these situations come down to simple misunderstandings, but this is also the nature of things and there isn't much you can do about it. 
